enue" rel="noopener nofollow">Massachusetts Department of Revenue</a>; the surtax threshold indexes annually and is confirmed for the current tax year before it drives any owner-comp or distribution record. TechBrot provides bookkeeping and QuickBooks work and coordinates with your CPA, EA, and the Massachusetts Department of Revenue; we do not file Massachusetts returns, the income tax or the 4% surtax, the corporate excise, the sales/use-tax return, the PFML return, or the PTE election, and do not represent clients before tax authorities.</p>
